{"title":"县委书记","authors":["段斌"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"县委书记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云南邓川焦石钢铁厂　段斌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县委书记李自荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙称他是神农。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年拍马攻新阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪枪挑的钢铁铜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风吹得树根翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛雨迷烟不见天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨之中人声叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座炉子歪半边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛟龙翻身猛抬头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记大步去挽救，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚跑到炉子边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石块掉下砸着头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血斑雨水湿战袍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄意志不动摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手砌炉子脸带笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过鲁班造仙桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难面前不低头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见铁水不甘休，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热心更比炉火旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧得炉炉铁水流。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}